.IX Title "CPANPLUS::Dist::MM 3pm"
.TH CPANPLUS::Dist::MM 3pm "2014-01-06" "perl v5.18.2" "Perl Programmers Reference Guide"
.\" For nroff, turn off justification.  Always turn off hyphenation; it makes
.\" way too many mistakes in technical documents.
.if n .ad l
